standard_location_load.query: SELECT *, sl_initial_distance AS sl_distance FROM wp_store_locator  WHERE   sl_latitude REGEXP '^[0-9]|-' AND sl_longitude REGEXP '^[0-9]|-'  AND  ( NOT sl_private OR sl_private IS NULL)   AND  ( (sl_initial_distance < 10000.000000 ) OR (sl_initial_distance IS NULL) )      ORDER BY sl_initial_distance asc LIMIT 500
